Package net.sf.mmm.client.ui.impl.gwt.widget.core.adapter Description

Contains the implementation for core widget adapters using GWT.

Client UI Impl GWT Widget Core Adapter

This package contains the implementation of UiWidgetAdapters for net.sf.mmm.client.ui.impl.gwt.widget.core using GWT (Google Web Toolkit).
